<span class="lbl">License + refund policy</span>
<h2 class="h2">The fine print</h2>
<ul class="ul">
<li><strong>Single-user license.</strong> One person at your company may use the workbook. For team/enterprise licenses, email us.</li>
<li><strong>No redistribution.</strong> Please don't post the file publicly or share it outside your business.</li>
<li><strong>Refund policy.</strong> 14-day refund, no questions asked. Email and we'll process it.</li>
<li><strong>Updates.</strong> v1 is the May 2026 edition. Future major versions may be paid upgrades; minor refreshes are free for previous buyers — email if you bought v1 and want the latest.</li>
</ul>
